videos.headline: Brown tosses 26-yard TD for BC's first score
videos.description: Anthony Brown tosses a 26-yard touchdown pass to Hunter Long to give Boston College the lead early.

videos.headline: Glines finds the corner for 2-yard Boston College TD
videos.description: Boston College takes an early 14-0 lead on Ben Glines' 2-yard touchdown run against Louisville.

videos.headline: Louisville's Cunningham streches for TD
videos.description: Malik Cunningham takes it himself on fourth down for a 1-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Louisville cuts the deficit with 3-yard TD
videos.description: Hassan Hall finds the edge on a 3-yard touchdown run to make it 14-13 Boston College.

videos.headline: Louisville QB uses read option en route to TD
videos.description: Jawon Pass finds a hole and runs for a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Louisville's Fitzpatrick makes ridiculous catch against his helmet
videos.description: Dez Fitzpatrick reaches back and pins the ball against his helmet, reminiscent of David Tyree's famous Super Bowl catch.

videos.headline: BC punches in 1-yard TD
videos.description: Boston College RB David Bailey slams in for a one-yard touchdown, extending the lead to 31-20 over Louisville.
